@startuml
[*] --> PowerOn
PowerOn --> [*]
PowerOn --> Startup
Startup --> Ready : everything is fine
Ready --> [*]
Ready --> Reset : reset pressed
Reset --> Ready
Ready --> Activate : activate pressed
Activate --> Monitoring : activated
Monitoring --> Alarm : sensor triggered
Alarm --> Monitoring : false alarm or time ends
Monitoring --> Ready : deactivated
Ready --> PowerOff : power off pressed
PowerOff --> Ready : power on pressed
@enduml
